msgctxt "15012"
msgid ""
"（江戸城へ将軍に直訴か……\n"
"　フッ。我ながら無茶な話だな）"
msgstr "(Is it a direct appeal to the shogun to Edo Castle?"

msgctxt "15071"
msgid ""
"（しかし山崎が口をふさがれたとは……\n"
"　まずは新選組の屯所に行ってみるか）"
msgstr ""
"(But Yamazaki's mouth was blocked ... First, why don't we go to the "
"Shinsengumi tunsho?)"

msgctxt "15147"
msgid ""
"「坂本龍馬」は今までずっと\n"
"倒幕戦争を引き起こすために動いてきた。"
msgstr "\"Ryoma Sakamoto\" has been working to cause a war of defeat."

msgctxt "15214"
msgid "その下準備が整ったらしい。"
msgstr "It seems that the preparations are ready."

msgctxt "15241"
msgid "どういうことだ？　なにかあったのか？"
msgstr "What does it mean? What happened?"

msgctxt "15278"
msgid "ああ……　薩摩の西郷と長州の桂が手を結んだ。"
msgstr "Ah ... Saigo of Satsuma and Katsura of Choshu joined hands."

msgctxt "15323"
msgid ""
"バラバラだった勤王の二大勢力が倒幕に向けて\n"
"秘密同盟を組んだんだ。"
msgstr "The two disjointed Qin Wangs formed a secret alliance for the defeat."

msgctxt "15390"
msgid "つまり……　「薩長同盟」だよ。"
msgstr "In other words ... It's the \"Satcho Alliance\"."

msgctxt "15421"
msgid "薩長同盟……？"
msgstr "The Samoan League...?"

msgctxt "15436"
msgid "そいつを仲立ちしたのも「坂本龍馬」って男らしい。"
msgstr "It seems that \"Ryoma Sakamoto\" was the man who mediated it."

msgctxt "15485"
msgid ""
"だが、この場合の「坂本龍馬」は……\n"
"例のあいつじゃねえ。お前さんだ。"
msgstr ""
"However, \"Ryoma Sakamoto\" in this case is ... not the usual one. You are."

msgctxt "15554"
msgid "なに？"
msgstr "What?"

msgctxt "15561"
msgid ""
"もっとも、そんときお前さんはシラフじゃ\n"
"なかったがな。"
msgstr "However, you weren't Shirafu at that time."

msgctxt "15616"
msgid "まさか……　あの夜の話か？"
msgstr "No way ... Is that the story of that night?"

msgctxt "15646"
msgid ""
"まったくよ、薩長のいがみ合いが\n"
"一晩の酒で水に流れちまうとは思わなかったよ。"
msgstr ""
"At all, I didn't expect Satsuma's quarrel to flow into the water with an "
"overnight drink."

msgctxt "15723"
msgid ""
"だがな……　そのバカバカしい話がこの国の内戦に\n"
"火をつけちまおうとしてる。"
msgstr ""
"But ... that ridiculous story is about to ignite the civil war in this "
"country."

msgctxt "15798"
msgid "そのきっかけを作ったのがお前さんだ。"
msgstr "You were the one who created the opportunity."

msgctxt "15844"
msgid ""
"そこへ来てもう一人の「坂本龍馬」が\n"
"火のついた薩長に油を注いでやがる。"
msgstr "Another \"Ryoma Sakamoto\" comes there and anoints the lit Satsumacho."

msgctxt "15915"
msgid "どうやって？"
msgstr "how?"

msgctxt "15928"
msgid ""
"やつはもう正真正銘の武器商人だ。\n"
"これまで以上に英国の武器を大量に薩長へ流してる。"
msgstr ""
"He's already a genuine weapons merchant. We are sending more British weapons"
" to Satsuma than ever before."

msgctxt "16011"
msgid "桂と西郷も倒幕戦の軍備に本腰入れ始めた。"
msgstr ""
"Katsura and Saigo also began to seriously engage in the military armament of"
" the defeat war."

msgctxt "16052"
msgid ""
"もういつドンパチ始まってもおかしくねえ。\n"
"関ヶ原以来の血が流れるぜ。"
msgstr ""
"It wouldn't be strange when the donpachi started. Blood has flowed since "
"Sekigahara."

msgctxt "16121"
msgid "倒幕戦争か……"
msgstr "Is it a defeat war ..."

msgctxt "16136"
msgid ""
"「坂本龍馬」は武器を売って大儲けするだろ。\n"
"日本人の血と引き換えにな。"
msgstr ""
"\"Ryoma Sakamoto\" will make a lot of money by selling weapons. In exchange "
"for Japanese blood."

msgctxt "16207"
msgid ""
"そして、開戦前夜のこの国を、よだれ垂らして\n"
"見てんのが西洋列強だ。"
msgstr ""
"And it is the Western powers who are drooling and watching this country on "
"the eve of the war."

msgctxt "16274"
msgid "となれば……　この俺もそろそろ動くしかねえやな。"
msgstr "Then ... I'm afraid I'll move soon."

msgctxt "16323"
msgid "あんた、まさか……　例の計画をやる気か？"
msgstr "You, no way ... are you motivated to plan the example?"

msgctxt "16364"
msgid ""
"ああ……　日本中が焼ける前に京の朝廷を滅ぼして\n"
"戦を止める。"
msgstr ""
"Ah ... Destroy the imperial court in Kyoto and stop the war before the whole"
" of Japan burns."

msgctxt "16425"
msgid "この国を列強の侵略から救うためだ。"
msgstr "This is to save this country from the invasion of the great powers."

msgctxt "16460"
msgid "本気で言っているのか？"
msgstr "Are you really saying it?"

msgctxt "16483"
msgid ""
"町の人間が何人焼け死ぬ？\n"
"侍だけじゃねえ、女も子供もだ。"
msgstr ""
"How many people in the town will burn to death? Not just samurai, but women "
"and children."

msgctxt "16540"
msgid ""
"それを焼き殺して、どの口が国を救うためだと\n"
"言える？"
msgstr "Can you say which mouth is to save the country by burning it?"

msgctxt "16593"
msgid ""
"何度も言わせるな。倒幕戦争が起きればもっと多くの\n"
"人間が死んだ挙句、異国に侵略される。"
msgstr ""
"Don't let me say it over and over. If a war of defeat occurs, more people "
"will die and they will be invaded by a foreign country."

msgctxt "16680"
msgid ""
"そもそもお前さんが薩長の仲を取り持ったせいだぜ。\n"
"おまけに寺田屋じゃあ例の「坂本龍馬」を\n"
"取り逃がした。"
msgstr ""
"It's because you got along with Satsuma in the first place. In addition, I "
"missed the usual \"Ryoma Sakamoto\" at Teradaya."

msgctxt "16785"
msgid "もう勢いづいた薩長を止めることはできねえ。"
msgstr "I can't stop the momentum of Satsuma."

msgctxt "16828"
msgid "……なら。薩長じゃなく、幕府を止めるってのは？"
msgstr "...... If. What about stopping the Bakufu instead of Satsumacho?"

msgctxt "16875"
msgid "幕府を、止める……？"
msgstr "Stop the shogunate ...?"

msgctxt "16896"
msgid ""
"ああ。幕府が……　仮にだが薩長に白旗を上げれば\n"
"戦争にはならないはずだ。"
msgstr ""
"Oh. If the shogunate raises a white flag to Satsuma, it shouldn't be a war."

msgctxt "16969"
msgid "幕府に白旗を上げさせるだぁ？"
msgstr "Let the shogunate raise the white flag, right?"

msgctxt "16998"
msgid "３００年、この国を支配してきた幕府にか？"
msgstr "Is it the shogunate that has ruled this country for 300 years?"

msgctxt "17048"
msgid ""
"いや……　待てよ、おい。\n"
"たしかにその手はあるかもしれねえな。"
msgstr "No ... wait, hey. Certainly there may be such a hand."

msgctxt "17111"
msgid ""
"薩長が戦争を引き起こす力を手に入れた\n"
"今だからこそ、徳川が聞く耳を持つってことも\n"
"あるか……"
msgstr ""
"Now that Satsuma has acquired the power to cause war, may Tokugawa have an "
"ear to hear ..."

msgctxt "17204"
msgid ""
"たとえばそうだな……\n"
"幕府の持つ政権を徳川将軍から帝に返させる。"
msgstr ""
"For example, that's right ... General Tokugawa returns the government of the"
" Shogunate to the emperor."

msgctxt "17269"
msgid "幕府の政権を、帝に……？"
msgstr "The administration of the Shogunate to the emperor ...?"

msgctxt "17294"
msgid "ああ……　「大政奉還」とでも言うのかな。"
msgstr "Ah ... I wonder if it's called \"Taisei Hokan\"."

msgctxt "17335"
msgid ""
"幕府がこの国の政権を手放せばもう薩長が\n"
"幕府相手に戦争を起こす理由はなくなる……"
msgstr ""
"If the Shogunate relinquishes the administration of this country, there is "
"no reason for Satsuma to start a war against the Shogunate ..."

msgctxt "17416"
msgid ""
"ここは、ひとつ将軍に直談判でもして、\n"
"白旗上げさせてみるか……？"
msgstr ""
"Would you like to have one general speak directly to raise the white flag "
"here ...?"

msgctxt "17481"
msgid "できるのか、そんなことが？"
msgstr "Can you do that?"

msgctxt "17508"
msgid ""
"できるワケねー。普通は、な……\n"
"だが……"
msgstr "I can do it. Normally ... but ..."

msgctxt "17549"
msgid "だが、なんだ。"
msgstr "But what?"

msgctxt "17564"
msgid ""
"斎藤一、いや坂本龍馬さんよ。\n"
"……あんただったらできるかもしれねぇ。"
msgstr "Saito Hajime, no, Ryoma Sakamoto. ...... You might be able to do it."

msgctxt "17633"
msgid "!?　俺が!?"
msgstr "!? I!?"

msgctxt "17644"
msgid ""
"これまで俺なりにアンタという人間を見てきたが、\n"
"アンタ以上に腕が立つ男はいねえ。"
msgstr "I've seen you as a person so far, but no one is better than you."

msgctxt "17725"
msgid ""
"それにアンタには、あの沖田みてえな男まで\n"
"動かしちまう魅力もある。"
msgstr ""
"Besides, you also have the charm of moving even that man who looks like "
"Okita."

msgctxt "17792"
msgid "なにを言ってるんだ。"
msgstr "What are you talking about?"

msgctxt "17813"
msgid "いやこれは本心だ。"
msgstr "No, this is the real intention."

msgctxt "17832"
msgid ""
"……今、もし江戸城にいる将軍様に忍びで会い、\n"
"しかも心動かすことができる男がいるとしたら、\n"
"アンタしかいねぇ。"
msgstr ""
"...... Now, if there is a man who can sneak up on the shogun in Edo Castle "
"and move his heart, you're the only one."

msgctxt "17943"
msgid ""
"なあ龍馬さんよ。\n"
"ここはひとつ、日本のために死ぬ覚悟で\n"
"江戸に行ってきちゃもらえねぇか？"
msgstr ""
"Hey Ryoma-san. Could you go to Edo here with the intention of dying for "
"Japan?"

msgctxt "18032"
msgid "俺が、江戸に……"
msgstr "I'm in Edo ..."

msgctxt "18049"
msgid ""
"ああ。江戸城には夜にでもなんとか忍び込むんだ。\n"
"もちろん、見つかりゃ殺される。"
msgstr ""
"Oh. I managed to sneak into Edo Castle even at night. Of course, if you find"
" it, you will be killed."

msgctxt "18128"
msgid "生きて帰るのは不可能に近い。"
msgstr "It's almost impossible to come back alive."

msgctxt "18157"
msgid ""
"だが将軍に「大政奉還」を直訴するとなると、\n"
"もうそれしかねえ。"
msgstr ""
"However, when it comes to directly appealing to the shogun for \"Taisei "
"Hokan,\" that is no longer the case."

msgctxt "18220"
msgid "将軍の寝床に忍び込むってことか……？"
msgstr "Do you mean to sneak into the general's bed ...?"

msgctxt "18257"
msgid "言いだしっぺはお前さんだぜ。"
msgstr "You're the one to say."

msgctxt "18286"
msgid ""
"それに、もしこの「大政奉還」を徳川が飲めば\n"
"もう一人の「坂本龍馬」も必ずなにか反応を見せる。"
msgstr ""
"Besides, if Tokugawa drinks this \"Taisei Hokan\", another \"Ryoma "
"Sakamoto\" will surely show some reaction."

msgctxt "18379"
msgid "どういうことだ？"
msgstr "What does it mean?"

msgctxt "18396"
msgid ""
"向こうは薩長を派手に引きこんで戦争の準備を\n"
"させてるんだ。"
msgstr ""
"The other side is pulling in the Satsuma chief to prepare for the war."

msgctxt "18455"
msgid "だが戦争ってのは準備だけでも相当の金がかかる。"
msgstr "However, it costs a lot of money just to prepare for a war."

msgctxt "18502"
msgid ""
"その邪魔をされたとなりゃ例の「坂本龍馬」は\n"
"黙っちゃいねえ。\n"
"必ずなにか動きを見せるはずだ。"
msgstr ""
"If you get in the way, the example \"Ryoma Sakamoto\" shouldn't be silent. "
"It must show some movement."

msgctxt "18604"
msgid "ま、無理にとは言わねえよ。"
msgstr "Well, don't say it's impossible."

msgctxt "18631"
msgid "そんときは計画通りに俺が京を焼くだけだ。"
msgstr "At that time, I just bake Kyo as planned."

msgctxt "18672"
msgid ""
"ただし、あんたがもう一人の「坂本龍馬」を\n"
"捕える機会はなくなるぜ。"
msgstr "However, you won't have a chance to catch another \"Ryoma Sakamoto\"."

msgctxt "18739"
msgid ""
"俺は……\n"
"前にも江戸に行ったが、城には登ったことがねえ。"
msgstr "I went to Edo before, but I never climbed the castle."

msgctxt "18796"
msgid "ちょうど一度中に入ってみてえと思ってた。"
msgstr "I thought I should go inside just once."

msgctxt "18837"
msgid ""
"いいんだな？\n"
"生きて帰ってくるだけでも奇跡なんだぜ？"
msgstr "Is that okay? Isn't it a miracle just to come back alive?"

msgctxt "18890"
msgid "ああ……　覚悟の上で言っている。"
msgstr "Ah ... I'm prepared to say it."

msgctxt "18923"
msgid ""
"フッフッフッ、上出来だ。\n"
"だが、まず新選組の幹部が１人で京を出たとなりゃ\n"
"人目をひく。"
msgstr ""
"Huff Huff, it's good. However, if the Shinsengumi executives leave Kyoto "
"alone, it will be noticeable."

msgctxt "19010"
msgid "江戸へ行くならひと晩待って夜明け前に発て。"
msgstr "If you go to Edo, wait overnight and leave before dawn."

msgctxt "19053"
msgid ""
"今日のところはいつもどおり屯所に\n"
"顔を出しておくんだな。"
msgstr "For now, I'm going to the tunsho as usual."

msgctxt "19110"
msgid ""
"屯所か。\n"
"……そうだな、ちょうど話を聞きたい相手もいる。"
msgstr ""
"Is it a tunsho? ...... Well, there are people who just want to hear the "
"story."

msgctxt "19167"
msgid "ん？"
msgstr "Hmm?"

msgctxt "19172"
msgid ""
"監察の山崎烝に例の「坂本龍馬」の息が\n"
"かかっているらしい。"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the inspector General Yamazaki Susumu is taking the breath of "
"the example \"Ryoma Sakamoto\"."

msgctxt "19231"
msgid "なるほど。だがそいつは……　一足遅かったぜ。"
msgstr "I see. But that was ... a little late."

msgctxt "19276"
msgid "なにがだ？"
msgstr "What is it?"

msgctxt "19287"
msgid "山崎はゆうべ、屯所にある土蔵の中で殺されてた。"
msgstr "Yamazaki was killed in a storehouse in the tunsho last night."

msgctxt "19334"
msgid "なんだと……!?"
msgstr "what……!?"

msgctxt "19349"
msgid ""
"お前さんが山崎の正体を知ったことで\n"
"口をふさがれたってことか……"
msgstr "Did you get blocked by knowing Yamazaki's true identity?"

msgctxt "19414"
msgid "もう一人の「坂本龍馬」の手の者にな。"
msgstr "Be the other person in the hands of \"Ryoma Sakamoto\"."

msgctxt "22948"
msgid "龍馬"
msgstr "Ryoma"

msgctxt "22953"
msgid "近藤"
msgstr "Kondo"
